                                        "textcolor": {
                                            "expression": "themecolor.theme_textcolor"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "text": "*This is a niche parameter that is likely not going to make a massive difference for most material types. However, for material that has prolonged sustain with only slightly louder hits going above it (cymbals are a good example of this), this can be the difference between hardly catching any onsets and catching every last one of them."
