                                            "expression": "themecolor.theme_textcolor"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "text": "In addition to fine tuning the macro parameters you can optimize the advanced settings. The on and off threshold allow you to fine tune the sensitivity parameter. The highpassfreq allows you to ignore frequencies that do not carry transient information. And you can optimize the slow and fast envelope follower settings to further fine tune the scales of time you are interested in extracting onsets from."
